dct_title_s: Upper Sylvan Lake restoration project, proposed dredging project
dct_description_sm: A map detailing a proposed dredging as part of a restoration project for Upper Sylvan Lake. Included in the map are current lake topography, surrounding land area designations, and inset maps for possible disposal sites for removed lake sediment.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
